---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy — YOUTUBE PLAYABLES" description="Privacy policy for YOUTUBE PLAYABLES — how we handle data, cookies, and local storage.">
  <a href="#main" class="skip-link">Skip to content</a>
  <main id="main" class="mx-auto max-w-[1400px] px-6 py-24">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-ink">Privacy Policy.</h1>
    <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-mute">Last updated: 2026-07-11</p>

    <div class="mt-8 space-y-6 text-body leading-7">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-ink">Overview</h2>
      <p>YOUTUBE PLAYABLES operates as a static gaming website. We do not require accounts to play, and we do not sell or share personal data.</p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-ink">Local storage</h2>
      <p>High scores, recently played games, and sound preferences are stored only in your browser’s local storage. We do not read or transmit this data.</p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-ink">Cookies</h2>
      <p>We do not use tracking cookies. Any cookies set are strictly necessary for site functionality or are managed by third-party hosting providers (for example, Vercel or CDN infrastructure).</p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-ink">Third-party services</h2>
      <p>We may use third-party fonts (Google Fonts) and hosting providers. Those providers may collect standard server logs under their own privacy policies.</p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-ink">Children’s privacy</h2>
      <p>Our games are suitable for all ages. We do not knowingly collect data from children under 13.</p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-ink">Changes</h2>
      <p>We may update this policy occasionally. Continued use of the site means you accept the updated policy.</p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-ink">Contact</h2>
      <p>For privacy questions, email <a href="mailto:calgroupofficial@gmail.com" class="text-link underline-offset-4 hover:underline">calgroupofficial@gmail.com</a>.</p>
    </div>

    <a href="/playables" class="mt-10 inline-block text-sm text-link underline-offset-4 hover:underline">← Back to playables</a>
  </main>
</Layout>
